    <header>
      <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-primary-cyan mb-2">Languages / Python Objects</p>
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">
        <Bilingual><span slot="zh">对象模型与内存管理</span><span slot="en">Object Model & Memory Management</span></Bilingual>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-ink-muted leading-relaxed">
        <Bilingual>
          <span slot="zh">"一切皆对象"是 Python 的核心设计——整数、函数、类、甚至类型本身都是堆上的 <code>PyObject</code>。这套模型的代价是<b>每个对象都有头部开销</b>：一个 <code>int</code> 在 C 里是 4 字节，在 Python 里是 28 字节。理解 <code>PyObject</code> 结构、类型系统（<code>PyTypeObject</code>）、以及<b>引用计数 + 分代 GC</b> 的双层回收机制——这些都写在 CPython 的 C 源码里——是后续性能优化的理论基础。点击下方查看对象内存布局。</span>
          <span slot="en">"Everything is an object" is Python's core design — ints, functions, classes, even types themselves are heap-allocated <code>PyObject</code>s. The cost: <b>every object has header overhead</b> — an <code>int</code> is 4 bytes in C but 28 in Python. Understanding the <code>PyObject</code> layout, type system (<code>PyTypeObject</code>), and the dual-layer <b>refcount + generational GC</b> reclamation — all written in CPython's C source — is the theoretical foundation for later optimization. Click below to explore object layout.</span>
        </Bilingual>
      </p>
    </header>

    <!-- 交互：PyObject 内存布局 -->
    <div class="glass p-5" data-viz="pyobj-layout">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2 mb-4">
        <button class="btn obj-btn btn-primary" data-obj="int"><span data-lang="zh">int</span><span data-lang="en">int</span></button>
        <button class="btn obj-btn" data-obj="list"><span data-lang="zh">list</span><span data-lang="en">list</span></button>
